<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>{{appName}} - New Login Detected</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
  {{> header}}
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h2>New Login Detected</h2>
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>We detected a new login to your {{appName}} account. Here are the details:</p>
    
    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{loginInfo.time}}</p>
      <p><strong>Device:</strong> {{loginInfo.device}}</p>
      <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{loginInfo.location}}</p>
      <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{loginInfo.ipAddress}}</p>
      {{#if loginInfo.isNewDevice}}
      <p style="color: #e74c3c;"><strong>⚠️ This is a new device</strong></p>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    
    <p>If this was you, you can ignore this email. If you don't recognize this activity, please secure your account immediately by changing your password.</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{securitySettingsUrl}}" style="background-color: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">Secure My Account</a>
    </div>
    
    <p>Thanks,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
  </div>
  {{> footer recipient=to}}
  
  <!-- Tracking pixel for email opens -->
  <img src="{{appUrl}}/api/email/track/{{emailId}}/open" alt="" width="1" height="1" style="display:none;">
</body>
</html>